info.desc: This is the room in Morril Hall you should be in.
info.instr: Go to the ground floor of Morrill Hall. Make your way towards the west-most point wall of the building.

info.desc: This is the doorway to Northrop Garage.
info.instr: Heading west there's a hallway. Straight ahead is a door with a sign going into Northrop Garage. Go through it.
Through there you'll be in Northrop Garage.
